      "rest_url": "https://townofdundee.com/wp-json/tribe/events/v1/events/10127",
      "title": "RFP 25-05 Mandatory Pre-Bid Meeting",
      "description": "<p><strong>RFP #25-05</strong></p>\n<p>Sealed proposals will be received by the Town of Dundee until <strong>4:00 P.M. on Wednesday, January 21, 2026,</strong>\u00a0at the Office of the Town Clerk located at 202 E. Main Street, for Road paving of Camp Endeavor Blvd. &amp; Lincoln Ave.</p>\n<p><strong>RFP 25-05 &#8211; </strong><strong>ROAD PAVING OF CAMP ENDEAVOR BLVD &amp; LINCOLN AVE</strong></p>\n<p>All questions regarding this solicitation must be received in writing no later than Wednesday, January 14, 2026, at 4:00 P.M. A Mandatory Pre-Bid meeting is scheduled for 9:00 A.M. Wednesday, January 7, 2026.\u00a0A Mandatory Site Visit is scheduled for 10:00 A.M. Wednesday, January 7, 2026. A Proposal Opening and Review is scheduled for Thursday, January 22, 2026, at 10:00 A.M.</p>\n<p>Copies of the RFP are available from the Town Clerk at Dundee Town Hall, 202 Main Street, Dundee, FL 33838 and at <a href=\"http://www.TownofDundee.com\">www.TownofDundee.com</a>.</p>",
